title: Biuletyn Instytutu Weterynarii w Puławach
aka: Bulletin de l'Institut Vétérinaire de Puławy
Bulletin of the Veterinary Institute in Puławy
additional-notes: This is a Polish publication. Its contents may still be copyrighted even without renewals or copyright notices, if they meet GATT copyright restoration requirements for works first published outside the US.

This journal primarily used its Polish title until 1962, and then primarily used the English title 'Bulletin of the Veterinary Institute in Puławy', until 2015.  (It then changed its title to 'Journal of Veterinary Research'.)
acknowledgement: Thanks to Scott F Andrews and Peter Sullivan for copyright research on this title.
